    "16604612272b74cc1f": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1660461227266cb95c-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What should you do if you hear noise disturbances?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "1660461227266cb95c-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Consistent noise disturbances can wreak havoc on your mental and physical state. Especially if the raucous noise is keeping you awake at night, which can lead to sleep deprivation and agitation.  <\/p><p>If you’re suffering from a noise disturbance, it’s only fair that you’ll want to take action. So let’s take a look at what you can do to counteract both community noise and public noise.  <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "b6b50ba2-ba34-4929-9818-326b6ce694c2": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Community noise",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1660461227266cb95c-0",
        "1660461227266cb95c-1",
        "b6b50ba2-ba34-4929-9818-326b6ce694c2"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 40,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    },
    "16581501774a32acf8": {
      "type": "loop-article-img-txt",
      "blocks": {
        "16581501770ad7ecad-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In most urban areas and communities, there will be ordinances that prohibit any excessive and unreasonable levels of noise. If somebody is consistently exceeding these ordinances, chances are that you will want to do something about it. But if your neighbor is the guilty party, it may not be the best idea to go straight to the nuclear option of filing a lawsuit.<\/p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "16581501770ad7ecad-1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Noise_disturbances.jpg",
        "image_3": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Noise_disturbances.jpg",
