    "166046188908e08637": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "166046188882d65dad-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Here are some steps you can take to try and tackle the situation:<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "166046188882d65dad-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Talk to them",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "92c1d27d-1a60-4fbe-b18b-18e6ec3ea987": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sometimes the best option is the easiest option. Rather than going straight to aggression, try and calmly approach your neighbor and inform them of the issue. There is a chance that they are unaware of the problem and can quickly remedy the situation.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "a2dda80f-6c78-4ab2-984a-ac9dfc9b040e": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Send a warning",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "ab1118a8-beda-4d52-a984-e4583a539e08": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>If talking to the guilty party didn’t lead anywhere, then you can send a written warning. This should include the noise laws and a statement of intent on how you plan to approach the situation if the noise doesn’t stop.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "166046188882d65dad-1",
        "166046188882d65dad-0",
