    "1663666726d37750dc": {
      "type": "loop-article-richtext",
      "blocks": {
        "bcf22ff2-ca78-43c9-b158-b7bccd8a412d": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I report a noise disturbance?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "166366672652e863a8-0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>If you’re concerned about the disruptive levels of noise in your community, then you can lodge a noise complaint with the police. <\/p><p>The police will most likely give the guilty party a verbal warning. If the noise continues then you can make a second complaint and further action could be taken.  <\/p><p>If you’re worried about any potential repercussions of reporting a disturbance, you can file your complaint anonymously. The police will not require you to leave any personal details, meaning you can take action while leaving your name out of it.  <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "b4e55a26-b471-41bf-906d-f07a1c531ed8": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Excessive noise is no joke",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "8dfa4a1b-079c-4694-b9a9-14a3ec1eb779": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Not only can noise disturbances increase your stress, anxiety, and agitation levels, but they can also hurt your ears. And while it’s important that you take action to counter these disturbances, realistically it may take some time.  <\/p><p>In the meantime, it’s important to protect your ears. Our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.loopearplugs.com\/products\/experience\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Experience<\/span><\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.loopearplugs.com\/products\/quiet\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Quiet<\/span><\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.loopearplugs.com\/products\/experience-pro\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Experience-Pro<\/span><\/a> earplugs are designed to not only protect your hearing but also help to reduce noise by up to 27 dB.  <\/p><p>Don’t let noise be a disturbance. Take action. Protect your hearing.  <\/p>"
          }
        },
